Resource Profile: Encounter - FR Encounter Document

Official URL: https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-encounter-document Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2026-02-04 Computable Name: FREncounterDocument

FREncounterDocument est un profil permettant de conserver les modalités d’une rencontre du patient. Il peut s’agir d’une rencontre passée ou à venir

Utilisations:

  • Référence ce Profil: DiagnosticReport - FR Diagnostic Report BIO chapter Document, Observation - FR Observation Administration Blood Derivatives Document, Observation - FR Blood Product Transfusion Document, Observation - FR Observation Contra Indications Document... Show 8 more, Observation - FR Observation Medical Summary Document, Observation - FR Observation Microorganism Detection Document, Observation - FR Observation Multiresistant Microorganisms Identification Document, Observation - FR Observation Pregnancy Document, Observation - FR Observation Result Document, Observation - FR Observation Transfusion Accidents Document, Observation - FR Observation Work Related Accident Document and Procedure - FR Procedure Act Document

Vous pouvez également vérifier les usages dans le FHIR IG Statistics

Binding: ActEncounterCode (extensible): Classification of the encounter.

Binding: JDV Modalite Sortie CISIS (preferred)
location S 0..1 BackboneElement Lieu d'exécution
modifierExtension ?!Σ 0..* Extension Extensions that cannot be ignored even if unrecognized
location 1..1 Reference(FR Location Document) Location the encounter takes place
